column10:
Years ago, I would've said Dark Souls is a fine game, but I no longer condone buying it for now; not only did Bandai Namco made the Prepare To Die Edition unobtainable, killing several Mods in the process (they should've done like Skyrim instead), but now they keep sponsoring bigoted Souls Creators on YouTube that buy Fake Views.

I'm being totally serious with the latter, I reported an asshole using View-Bots, which have very similar patterns across a wide range of users, for years to boost his viewership and harassing those that don't even interact with him, yet Bandai, making some of the most hyped games with huge teams behind them, could never see what I, all on my own, had seen?  They couldn't see the many "Thanks for your Souls Playthroughs!" in a DOOM Eternal Let's Play, amongst many other things, like WTF, this is mad if true.

Really now;
