These NINE Bots all stole from [u][url=https://www.youtube.com/@bIuecrimson]bluecrimson[/url][/u], whom made these Videos 9 years ago, and look at the Channel Creation Dates of the last 4 on that list, they were made in February 2020 and only 6 days apart at most from one and another.  I had witnessed yet more stupid garbage like this, so much I'm still making a Series out of it.  This is the type of crap Bandai is unable to see, really?  I can't make it more obvious something's off, they're condoning it like YouTube is what this is.

Also, they keep putting out utterly bad products like Jump Force.  It's not FromSoftware I may have issues with, but I no longer have faith Bandai Namco has the best intentions anymore, they are like the others, taking advantage of the system of awful Influencers on SheeTube to promote garbage and/or using the bad clout as it's still good clout and publicity.  They're condoning an atmosphere that has made it impossible for those being earnest to even get a chance to strive.  Do not support them, Gaming truly has become a billboard for shit.

You will die a lot but it will feel really good at the end;
Amazing boss fights;
Perfect level design with lots of impressive conections between areas;
Lots of weapon variety;
No "hand-helding";
Really immersive athmosphere;
lots of secrets.

Man, it does have it all.
